Package ui.controller.manageBalance

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChooseBankAccountController
    Controller of the chooseBankAccountView called when the current user has to choose a BankAccount to recover his balance or a part of it.
    ChooseCreditCardController
    Controller of the chooseCreditCardView called when the current user has to choose a CreditCard to refill his balance.
    ChooseRecoverAmountController
    Controller of the chooseRecoverAmountView called when the current user has to choose a amount of money to recover on his BankAccount.
    ChooseRefillAmountController
    Controller of the chooseRefillAmountView called when the current user has to choose a amount of money to refill his balance with the selected CreditCard.
    ManageBalanceController
    Controller of the manageBalanceView called when the current user want to manage his balance.
